data.description: All Brick Ranch with a Mid Century Modern Flare & it has so many entertaining spaces. This hidden gem has so much room! Multiple Living Rooms with Fireplaces, Formal Dining with Beautiful Wood Built Ins & Butler Door. If you love Pocket Doors, this home has a few. Workshop with ample space to get crafty. Greenroom in Basement and Library. A back patio that is made for hosting! This gem just needs a refresh to be the showstopper that it deserves to be again. The circle drive and huge parking pad will be perfect for all those party guests. Sold As Is.
